The paper also introduces a probabilistic deductive database, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The use of message-passing and belief propagation is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL), which is also mentioned in the paper. Finally, the paper discusses the efficiency and performance of the proposed system, which could fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
